15:47.829 --> 15:48.868
I feel like throwing up.

15:51.548 --> 15:53.469
Why did you drink so much?

15:54.268 --> 15:54.748
No.

15:55.388 --> 15:57.268
Why did you drink so much?

15:57.589 --> 15:59.069
Wait, why is there

15:59.069 --> 15:59.949
a stranger?

16:00.109 --> 16:00.908
It's so late now.

16:00.949 --> 16:02.788
Staying out this late?

16:03.189 --> 16:03.628
Get out.

16:04.829 --> 16:05.508
Who are you?

16:05.788 --> 16:07.028
Who are you?

16:07.788 --> 16:08.508
Call the police!

16:08.788 --> 16:10.788
This is my bar!

16:11.388 --> 16:12.709
This is my bar!

16:12.788 --> 16:13.949
Why call the police?

16:13.989 --> 16:15.349
This is my house.

16:15.508 --> 16:16.628
This is my house.

16:16.628 --> 16:17.189
My house!

16:17.309 --> 16:17.989
My house!

16:18.109 --> 16:18.709
Mine!

16:19.189 --> 16:20.268
Why did you bring her here?

16:20.309 --> 16:21.508
- They're fighting now!
- Want a fight?

16:21.508 --> 16:22.349
- Think I wanted this?
- Alright.

16:22.788 --> 16:23.589
She insisted on

16:23.589 --> 16:24.388
going here.

16:24.429 --> 16:25.109
What could I do?

16:26.109 --> 16:27.388
Stop making things up.

16:27.628 --> 16:28.349
Not that dramatic.

16:28.349 --> 16:29.429
I'm just telling

16:29.668 --> 16:30.429
the truth,

16:30.668 --> 16:31.788
or I'll take your last name.

16:32.388 --> 16:33.628
But you lost your surname.

16:34.788 --> 16:35.309
Well...

16:36.748 --> 16:37.628
That means

16:37.908 --> 16:39.148
you two stayed here

16:39.229 --> 16:40.229
last night, right?

16:42.189 --> 16:43.028
It's because you two

16:43.429 --> 16:44.309
were unpredictable!

16:44.829 --> 16:46.668
One second you're enemies...

16:46.748 --> 16:47.508
The next

16:47.668 --> 16:48.709
you were inseparable.

16:49.949 --> 16:50.709
I want to throw up.

16:51.349 --> 16:52.748
Put me down!

16:53.109 --> 16:53.748
I'm warning you,

16:54.189 --> 16:55.028
I'll count to three.

16:55.148 --> 16:56.069
Put me down now!

16:56.229 --> 16:56.748
Go ahead.

16:57.189 --> 16:57.668
Three.

17:02.748 --> 17:03.388
Three.

17:06.108 --> 17:06.669
Three.

17:08.068 --> 17:08.588
Yan! Yan!

17:08.588 --> 17:09.469
Be careful.

17:10.669 --> 17:11.389
Be careful.

17:12.508 --> 17:13.149
I'm dizzy.

17:13.629 --> 17:14.268
Honey.

17:16.588 --> 17:17.508
You're so beautiful.

17:17.548 --> 17:19.229
Honey, you're so manly.

17:20.949 --> 17:22.308
You're finally back.

17:22.828 --> 17:23.548
Did you hear

17:23.548 --> 17:25.308
me calling your name?

17:25.629 --> 17:27.429
I knew it was you calling me.

17:28.669 --> 17:29.669
Good that you heard.

17:32.189 --> 17:32.909
Let's go.

17:33.788 --> 17:34.308
Wait!

17:36.469 --> 17:37.028
Put me down!

17:37.588 --> 17:38.308
Now!

17:39.788 --> 17:42.068
Who is this?

17:43.308 --> 17:44.709
Where is my wedding photo?

17:46.308 --> 17:47.909
Whose back is this?

17:48.469 --> 17:49.909
Don't rush. Wait for me.

17:56.828 --> 17:58.548
This is my back.

18:00.588 --> 18:02.308
No. Don't try to fool me.

18:02.669 --> 18:03.788
This one is slimmer.

18:04.389 --> 18:05.028
See?

18:06.348 --> 18:09.068
The shoulders
are much leaner than yours.

18:09.308 --> 18:09.989
Understand?

18:10.389 --> 18:12.068
This was before I built muscle.

18:13.068 --> 18:13.629
This...

18:15.429 --> 18:16.348
I am

18:17.588 --> 18:19.229
facing my wife.

18:20.548 --> 18:22.108
Right here.

18:23.508 --> 18:24.949
My wife is so beautiful.

18:25.788 --> 18:26.869
Right here.

18:28.028 --> 18:28.669
Honey.

18:29.268 --> 18:29.828
Come.

18:32.068 --> 18:34.108
First pan-fry the tuna.

18:34.508 --> 18:35.068
Okay?

18:35.909 --> 18:38.268
Golden brown on both sides, okay?

18:39.828 --> 18:40.268
Hungry.

18:40.709 --> 18:41.788
Should be fine now.

18:43.548 --> 18:45.108
Which one do you want?

18:47.469 --> 18:47.989
This one?

18:48.788 --> 18:49.828
The one that just swam by.

18:49.949 --> 18:50.469
This one?

18:50.629 --> 18:51.949
That one! That one!

18:52.149 --> 18:53.828
They aren't sober at all.

18:54.669 --> 18:55.949
What if something

18:55.949 --> 18:56.308
happens?

18:56.709 --> 18:58.149
Maybe we should stay.

18:58.348 --> 18:58.949
Makes sense.

18:59.748 --> 19:00.748
I'm afraid they'd really

19:00.869 --> 19:01.629
eat live fish.

19:02.268 --> 19:03.149
I want to eat it.

19:10.828 --> 19:11.508
Don't!

19:12.548 --> 19:13.268
Not here.

19:14.068 --> 19:14.869
It's cold here.

19:14.989 --> 19:16.028
- You'll catch cold.
- Don't.

19:16.108 --> 19:16.588
Don't.

19:16.828 --> 19:17.548
Go to the bedroom.

19:17.629 --> 19:18.548
Where's the bedroom?

19:18.548 --> 19:19.028
Bedroom!

19:21.788 --> 19:22.709
You know what?

19:23.348 --> 19:24.588
You two were too wild.

19:25.028 --> 19:25.508
Right there,

19:26.108 --> 19:27.989
you kept taking
clothes off and touching.

19:28.149 --> 19:29.108
We were worried you'd

19:29.189 --> 19:30.308
catch cold,

19:30.709 --> 19:31.788
so we sent you upstairs.

19:31.788 --> 19:32.828
But you still did wild.

19:34.949 --> 19:35.268
Fine.

19:36.389 --> 19:37.028
Then stop.

19:37.189 --> 19:37.548
Right.

19:37.828 --> 19:39.389
I'm getting a break. I'll take her out.

19:39.389 --> 19:39.669
Right.

19:39.709 --> 19:41.108
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

19:41.548 --> 19:42.949
I want to go out too.

19:43.429 --> 19:44.989
You? You go with him.

19:45.028 --> 19:45.909
I need to go date.

19:46.068 --> 19:46.748
I'm leaving. Bye.

19:46.788 --> 19:47.588
Let's go.

19:53.229 --> 19:54.629
Shall we...

19:56.548 --> 19:57.588
I need to work today.

20:00.268 --> 20:01.068
Me too.

20:07.189 --> 20:08.989
Did I bring my bag yesterday?

20:11.028 --> 20:11.788
I'll look for it.

20:12.229 --> 20:12.748
Thanks.

20:16.268 --> 20:17.429
Can't be here.

20:18.508 --> 20:19.308
I'll look for it.

20:24.189 --> 20:24.709
This...

20:25.149 --> 20:25.588
Nothing.

20:25.748 --> 20:26.268
No?

20:26.748 --> 20:27.788
Not here either?

20:28.068 --> 20:28.588
Let me see.

20:33.788 --> 20:34.308
Over there.

20:35.028 --> 20:35.508
There.

20:37.669 --> 20:38.149
Right.

20:44.469 --> 20:45.268
Found it.

20:46.189 --> 20:46.869
Hard to find.

20:46.869 --> 20:47.909
Well...

20:48.629 --> 20:49.429
I'm leaving.

20:52.548 --> 20:54.189
Want to grab a meal before that?

20:57.229 --> 20:57.828
Sounds good.

21:00.669 --> 21:01.669
What would you like?

21:02.748 --> 21:03.429
Anything is fine.

21:05.469 --> 21:05.989
Like what?

21:08.869 --> 21:09.629
Haoming.

21:09.869 --> 21:11.149
I bought you food.

21:11.348 --> 21:12.348
Are you home?

21:25.389 --> 21:25.949
She left.

21:33.108 --> 21:33.669
Yes.

21:38.629 --> 21:39.548
I am still here.

21:46.508 --> 21:47.548
Morning, Mom.

21:48.909 --> 21:49.348
Look.

21:49.389 --> 21:49.909
This is good.

21:49.909 --> 21:50.429
Quite sturdy.

21:51.828 --> 21:53.028
We're doing

21:53.149 --> 21:53.709
exercises.

21:55.508 --> 21:56.189
Tricep training.

21:56.189 --> 21:57.149
Very good.

21:58.788 --> 21:59.068
Nice.

21:59.108 --> 21:59.588
Well done.

21:59.909 --> 22:00.348
Work?

22:00.348 --> 22:00.869
Great.

22:01.268 --> 22:01.788
Go to work.

22:01.788 --> 22:02.189
Work.

22:02.469 --> 22:03.189
Okay, me too.

22:04.429 --> 22:04.909
Pants.

22:06.949 --> 22:07.828
I'm going to work out.

22:08.588 --> 22:09.229
He's so cute.

22:09.229 --> 22:10.469
Mom, want to work out?

22:10.469 --> 22:11.068
- Work out.
- Yes.

22:12.508 --> 22:13.548
I bought some breakfast.

22:13.949 --> 22:14.909
How about...

22:17.108 --> 22:17.469
Perfect.

22:17.669 --> 22:18.788
Let me help you, Mom.

22:19.588 --> 22:21.028
I'll help.

22:31.788 --> 22:32.588
Yan, eat this.

22:33.348 --> 22:34.149
I think

22:34.189 --> 22:35.229
it's your favorite.

22:35.669 --> 22:36.389
Have a few more.

22:40.989 --> 22:41.508
Yan.

22:41.989 --> 22:43.696
Congratulations
on winning the competition.

22:43.989 --> 22:44.748
Haoming

22:44.748 --> 22:46.108
has been happy for you about this.

22:47.189 --> 22:47.828
Right, Haoming?

22:49.748 --> 22:50.189
Yes.

22:50.548 --> 22:52.308
Actually, Haoming has helped me a lot,

22:53.308 --> 22:54.709
so I should thank him.

22:58.389 --> 22:59.229
There's something

22:59.229 --> 23:00.189
I need your help with.

23:01.909 --> 23:04.028
Haochen has advanced
in his equestrian competition.

23:04.229 --> 23:05.229
He wants to hold

23:05.268 --> 23:06.629
a home party.

23:07.268 --> 23:08.748
You know him best.

23:09.108 --> 23:10.028
Could you help me

23:10.149 --> 23:10.949
and plan it out?

23:13.828 --> 23:14.508
No problem.

23:14.989 --> 23:15.788
I'll make a plan

23:15.909 --> 23:17.108
and send you then.

23:17.669 --> 23:17.909
Mom.

23:17.949 --> 23:19.068
Ask Haochen

23:19.149 --> 23:20.068
if he has any ideas,

23:20.429 --> 23:20.869
okay?

23:21.469 --> 23:22.788
Why don't you just come home

23:22.788 --> 23:23.389
and handle it?

23:24.028 --> 23:25.068
Haochen would be thrilled

23:25.068 --> 23:25.909
to see you back.

23:26.469 --> 23:27.588
So is Haoming.

23:27.949 --> 23:28.429
Right?

23:33.268 --> 23:34.669
I'll check my schedule.

23:36.028 --> 23:36.828
It's settled then.

23:41.429 --> 23:42.588
This is also your favorite.

23:44.108 --> 23:44.548
Mom.

23:45.108 --> 23:46.669
I really need to go to work

23:46.709 --> 23:47.348
today.

23:48.828 --> 23:50.389
I haven't even freshened up...

23:51.669 --> 23:52.389
For the files.

23:54.909 --> 23:55.869
Well...

23:55.869 --> 23:57.028
take your time.

23:57.429 --> 23:58.189
I'm leaving.

24:00.268 --> 24:00.669
Well...

24:01.828 --> 24:03.068
Haoming, see Yan out.

24:03.108 --> 24:03.469
No need.

24:04.669 --> 24:06.429
Stay here and finish your meal.

24:06.788 --> 24:07.308
Okay.

24:08.588 --> 24:10.149
What? Just go!

24:35.389 --> 24:35.949
Hot?

24:38.828 --> 24:39.429
No.

24:41.629 --> 24:42.508
Need the AC?

24:43.028 --> 24:43.588
No.

24:43.748 --> 24:44.108
Okay.

24:51.788 --> 24:53.108
Play some music?

24:53.989 --> 24:54.548
Okay.

25:18.189 --> 25:19.268
Let's turn it off.

25:27.028 --> 25:28.308
My mom's always been like this.

25:29.268 --> 25:30.429
Speaks her mind,

25:30.828 --> 25:31.788
without caring others.

25:32.268 --> 25:32.909
Well,

25:33.389 --> 25:34.189
I think it's nice.

25:34.828 --> 25:35.909
Be open and honest,

25:37.348 --> 25:38.588
never hiding feelings.

25:55.108 --> 25:55.909
- Right, you...
- Right, you...

25:58.308 --> 25:58.989
You first.

26:00.389 --> 26:01.989
How's Yan Studio lately?

26:04.268 --> 26:04.709
Good.

26:06.588 --> 26:08.028
After the competition,

26:09.108 --> 26:10.429
our sales are back to normal.

26:10.869 --> 26:12.348
So our third batch

26:12.348 --> 26:13.508
is being produced now.

26:15.068 --> 26:15.989
Great.

26:16.629 --> 26:17.709
People have

26:17.828 --> 26:19.308
high recognition for handmade brocade

26:19.348 --> 26:20.149
right now.

26:20.588 --> 26:21.469
Then what's

26:21.469 --> 26:22.429
your next plan?

26:24.429 --> 26:26.588
I want to develop more projects

26:26.828 --> 26:29.229
about traditional dyeing techniques.

26:29.909 --> 26:30.949
For example,

26:31.989 --> 26:32.709
Shu brocade.

26:34.229 --> 26:34.828
Heard of it?

26:38.068 --> 26:39.024
Gambiered Canton gauze,

26:39.949 --> 26:40.548
grass cloth.

26:41.989 --> 26:42.669
Moreover,

26:42.949 --> 26:45.068
I want to create a new series

26:45.229 --> 26:47.389
about botanical dyeing technique.

26:48.189 --> 26:49.508
I think it would be unique.

26:49.949 --> 26:50.629
But this

26:50.629 --> 26:51.828
requires training.

26:52.588 --> 26:53.068
Wonderful.

26:54.469 --> 26:55.909
What did you want to ask me?

26:57.108 --> 26:58.189
I wanted to ask you

26:58.828 --> 27:00.909
if your collaboration with Mr. Baraikin

27:01.429 --> 27:01.909
goes well.

27:03.068 --> 27:03.869
Very well.

27:04.389 --> 27:04.869
Also,

27:05.709 --> 27:06.869
Mrs. Baraikin

27:07.348 --> 27:08.629
is very concerned about you.

27:11.909 --> 27:12.429
Right.

27:14.748 --> 27:16.348
I should properly thank her,

27:16.348 --> 27:17.348
but I've been too busy.

27:20.508 --> 27:21.788
Are you free tomorrow evening?

27:25.108 --> 27:26.268
I'll invite them for dinner.

27:29.508 --> 27:29.989
Sure.

27:30.909 --> 27:31.588
I'll treat them.

27:31.869 --> 27:32.588
No,

27:32.669 --> 27:33.629
my treat this time.

27:34.108 --> 27:36.108
Tomorrow at 6 PM.
I'll text you the address.

27:37.469 --> 27:37.788
Okay.

27:40.389 --> 27:42.229
I wonder if Mr. Baraikin

27:42.308 --> 27:44.068
prefers domestic or imported liquor.

27:45.028 --> 27:46.308
I'll prepare both.

27:49.508 --> 27:50.508
Are we drinking tomorrow?

27:51.788 --> 27:52.429
Of course.

27:53.189 --> 27:53.949
Last time,

27:53.949 --> 27:54.909
he and I didn't enjoy.

27:55.308 --> 27:55.989
Let me tell you,

27:56.429 --> 27:57.548
alcohol is wonderful.

27:57.709 --> 27:58.548
After drinking,

27:58.828 --> 28:00.149
it brings us closer

28:00.629 --> 28:01.348
and builds bond.

28:06.308 --> 28:07.788
You shouldn't drink tomorrow.

28:10.548 --> 28:11.429
I can handle it.

28:21.788 --> 28:22.548
Gas it up.

28:25.108 --> 28:26.108
I definitely will.

28:32.389 --> 28:33.588
I mean your car.

28:53.028 --> 28:53.869
We've confirmed

28:53.869 --> 28:55.028
the details with the factory.

28:55.268 --> 28:56.268
They'll prioritize

28:56.308 --> 28:57.229
producing our line.

28:57.548 --> 28:58.709
The release date

28:58.748 --> 28:59.669
can likely be moved up.

29:01.588 --> 29:02.748
And 30 percent deposit?

29:03.828 --> 29:05.149
The factory manager

29:05.268 --> 29:06.548
has changed attitudes.

29:06.909 --> 29:07.989
Now he's eager to keep us.

29:08.828 --> 29:09.989
The award changed everything.

29:11.268 --> 29:12.068
So,

29:12.709 --> 29:14.108
we need to improve and stay strong.

29:14.989 --> 29:15.989
Once we are stronger,

29:17.308 --> 29:18.629
the world smiles at us.

29:23.068 --> 29:24.469
Monitor the factory closely.

29:25.108 --> 29:25.588
No problem.

29:25.869 --> 29:26.909
Let's end here for today.

29:27.989 --> 29:28.588
Head back early

29:28.828 --> 29:29.909
- and get some rest.
- Alright.

29:30.788 --> 29:32.229
I'll review this with you.

29:33.149 --> 29:33.709
Bye.

29:34.548 --> 29:35.429
Are you busy tonight?

29:36.548 --> 29:37.028
Yes.

29:41.508 --> 29:42.028
Hello.

29:43.788 --> 29:44.748
Who's the person

29:44.748 --> 29:45.348
in charge?

29:46.028 --> 29:46.508
Hello.

29:46.989 --> 29:47.669
I'm Xu Yan.

29:48.189 --> 29:49.268
Let me introduce myself.

29:50.108 --> 29:51.308
I'm Zhang Fengyu,

29:51.629 --> 29:53.909
Director of the Economic Service Center
of Gubei Town.

29:54.189 --> 29:55.108
My business card.

29:55.588 --> 29:56.068
Okay.

29:56.348 --> 29:57.548
I heard about you won

29:57.748 --> 29:58.389
the competition

29:58.709 --> 29:59.588
and came to visit.

30:00.348 --> 30:01.469
Here to place orders?

30:02.788 --> 30:03.508
Actually,

30:04.028 --> 30:05.268
I'm not here to purchase.

30:06.108 --> 30:07.108
Let me tell you

30:07.189 --> 30:08.229
the purpose of my visit.

30:09.469 --> 30:10.788
This is Gubei Town's

30:12.268 --> 30:12.828
brochure.

30:12.909 --> 30:13.508
(Gubei Town)
Take a look.

30:14.669 --> 30:15.788
This is the leaflet

30:16.709 --> 30:18.229
of our botanical dyeing technique.

30:18.389 --> 30:18.949
Take a look.

30:23.108 --> 30:25.748
Gubei Town specializes
in botanical dyeing,

30:26.229 --> 30:27.548
an intangible cultural heritage.

30:28.108 --> 30:29.629
We know you've helped promote

30:29.629 --> 30:31.268
the handmade brocade.

30:31.268 --> 30:31.909
I wonder

30:32.268 --> 30:33.548
if you could

30:34.068 --> 30:35.909
help promote our botanical dyeing.

30:37.068 --> 30:38.588
We are about

30:38.588 --> 30:39.508
to develop this series.

30:42.669 --> 30:43.469
I was right to come!

30:44.108 --> 30:44.828
Wonderful!

30:44.909 --> 30:46.229
To be honest,

30:46.909 --> 30:47.548
for promoting

30:47.748 --> 30:48.909
Gubei Town's tourism,

30:49.308 --> 30:49.828
we plan

30:50.229 --> 30:51.949
to invite influencers

30:51.989 --> 30:52.788
to come for a tour.

30:53.788 --> 30:54.469
We want more

30:54.469 --> 30:55.308
promotional angles.

30:55.588 --> 30:56.028
But

30:57.149 --> 30:57.748
I trust you

30:58.108 --> 30:59.629
on promoting the botanical dyeing.

31:01.629 --> 31:02.229
Thank you.

31:02.909 --> 31:04.469
Mr. Zhang, thank you

31:05.068 --> 31:06.308
for your trust in Yan Studio.

31:07.149 --> 31:08.588
We're deeply interested in

31:09.028 --> 31:09.989
the botanical dyeing.

31:11.028 --> 31:12.308
We'll contact you later

31:12.429 --> 31:13.389
for the details.

31:15.308 --> 31:16.869
I need to study more

31:16.909 --> 31:18.788
about botanical dyeing.

31:19.028 --> 31:19.429
Ms. Xu.

31:20.028 --> 31:21.828
We have botanical dyeing workshops.

31:22.149 --> 31:23.149
Just come.

31:23.389 --> 31:24.949
I'll arrange hands-on sessions for you.

31:25.348 --> 31:25.669
Right.

31:26.308 --> 31:27.268
This is Gubei Town's

31:27.548 --> 31:28.308
invitation letter.

31:28.429 --> 31:28.909
Here.

31:28.989 --> 31:29.348
Okay.

31:29.814 --> 31:32.816
(Invitation)

31:33.389 --> 31:34.108
Thank you so much.

31:34.548 --> 31:35.588
No, thank you so much.

31:36.028 --> 31:36.788
I'm leaving then.

31:37.709 --> 31:38.949
- I'll see you out.
- No need.

31:38.949 --> 31:39.629
Don't bother.

31:40.108 --> 31:40.828
See you in town.

31:42.229 --> 31:42.949
- Bye.
- Take care.

31:44.629 --> 31:46.189
Perfect timing.

31:47.268 --> 31:48.469
Things go smoothly.

31:51.028 --> 31:51.389
Right.

31:51.869 --> 31:52.989
Sort out all the materials

31:53.068 --> 31:54.229
we collected about

31:54.469 --> 31:55.149
botanical dyeing,

31:55.149 --> 31:56.028
and hold a meeting.

31:56.348 --> 31:56.828
Okay.

32:00.348 --> 32:00.828
Ms. Xu.

32:01.548 --> 32:01.949
Let's go.

32:02.508 --> 32:03.108
Where to?

32:03.429 --> 32:05.108
An excellent Yunnan cuisine restaurant.

32:05.149 --> 32:06.189
Let's go try it today.

32:08.788 --> 32:09.588
I have plans.

32:11.068 --> 32:11.588
I'm leaving.

32:13.709 --> 32:14.189
Leaving?

32:16.429 --> 32:17.669
Then Ms. Qiao, shall we go?

32:17.909 --> 32:18.588
I have plans too.

32:21.588 --> 32:21.949
Wait,

32:22.508 --> 32:23.389
only us have no plans?

32:23.748 --> 32:24.669
Apparently.

32:56.869 --> 32:58.149
This place is gorgeous.

32:59.669 --> 33:00.869
Stunning.

33:03.189 --> 33:03.669
You're here.

33:04.869 --> 33:05.548
Nice to meet you.

33:06.149 --> 33:06.709
Same here.

33:06.748 --> 33:07.308
Welcome.

33:07.308 --> 33:08.788
Mr. Shen, we meet again.

33:08.909 --> 33:09.268
Hello.

33:09.709 --> 33:10.469
Everything's ready.

33:10.869 --> 33:11.748
Okay, thanks.

33:30.508 --> 33:30.989
Thank you.

33:53.669 --> 33:54.348
Hello.

33:54.748 --> 33:56.028
In a hurry to go to the banquet?

33:56.429 --> 33:56.949
Miss Xu.

34:09.429 --> 34:10.309
What's the matter,

34:10.349 --> 34:10.869
Steve?

34:13.548 --> 34:14.349
I want to give you

34:14.349 --> 34:15.228
a friendly warning.

34:15.949 --> 34:16.708
No need,

34:16.829 --> 34:17.188
thanks.

34:18.028 --> 34:19.108
Don't you want to know

34:19.269 --> 34:20.309
why Shen Haoming

34:20.309 --> 34:21.269
invited you here?

34:23.829 --> 34:24.349
Networking?

34:25.269 --> 34:26.269
Or acting with him?

34:27.708 --> 34:28.429
Seems like

34:28.548 --> 34:29.869
Shen Haoming

34:29.909 --> 34:30.989
has deceived you.

34:31.869 --> 34:32.909
Perhaps you don't know

34:33.429 --> 34:36.188
Baraikin set a three-month
evaluation period for Jinda Group.

34:36.909 --> 34:38.228
When Yan Studio was in trouble,

34:38.548 --> 34:39.588
he tried everything

34:39.588 --> 34:40.588
to help you.

34:41.548 --> 34:42.548
Have you ever considered

34:44.108 --> 34:45.628
he did all that

34:46.469 --> 34:47.668
merely to keep you

34:47.949 --> 34:49.028
from divorce?

34:50.068 --> 34:51.068
Everything he did

34:51.909 --> 34:53.148
was just for business,

34:54.188 --> 34:54.909
not out of love.

34:55.108 --> 34:57.068
How long will you stay
in Jingzhou this time?

34:57.469 --> 34:58.108
Actually,

34:58.108 --> 34:59.148
I came with my husband.

34:59.628 --> 35:00.749
He's here to discuss

35:00.749 --> 35:02.188
a collaboration project.

35:02.429 --> 35:02.829
Right,

35:03.508 --> 35:04.228
Haoming's company

35:04.309 --> 35:05.508
is on our shortlist

35:05.508 --> 35:06.429
for the collaboration.

35:06.548 --> 35:07.389
However,

35:07.389 --> 35:08.469
all companies will face

35:08.508 --> 35:09.708
a three-month evaluation.

35:11.869 --> 35:13.188
Then I'll wait

35:13.188 --> 35:13.749
for good news.

35:16.869 --> 35:18.789
Shen Haoming said

35:19.028 --> 35:20.228
to love and support his wife

35:20.548 --> 35:21.869
in the interview.

35:22.228 --> 35:23.309
It was genuinely touching.

35:23.749 --> 35:25.309
If there were a business world Oscar,

35:25.588 --> 35:26.628
he'd undoubtedly win it.

35:27.148 --> 35:27.469
Right,

35:27.869 --> 35:29.309
after Shen Haoming got interviewed,

35:29.389 --> 35:30.469
Jinda Group's stock

35:30.469 --> 35:31.588
hit the upper limit twice.

35:31.829 --> 35:33.068
I think investors

35:33.668 --> 35:34.829
eagerly want to see

35:34.989 --> 35:36.429
a loving couple

35:36.829 --> 35:38.789
supporting each other.

35:39.349 --> 35:40.429
Mr. Shen has

35:40.628 --> 35:41.588
helped you,

35:41.829 --> 35:42.749
caught the attention

35:42.749 --> 35:43.429
of the Baraikins,

35:43.708 --> 35:44.588
and profited

35:44.628 --> 35:45.429
from stock gains.

35:46.269 --> 35:47.269
A triple victory indeed.

35:48.028 --> 35:48.949
So impressed.

35:49.309 --> 35:50.349
As far as I know,

35:50.749 --> 35:51.909
today's dinner

35:52.588 --> 35:54.068
aims to convince the Baraikins

35:54.068 --> 35:55.349
that you two

35:55.469 --> 35:56.349
are a loving couple.

35:59.548 --> 36:00.949
He even hired someone

36:01.829 --> 36:02.789
to take pictures

36:02.789 --> 36:03.588
of you nearby

36:04.188 --> 36:05.389
and publish romantic snippets.

36:05.508 --> 36:06.389
Giving his all out!

36:08.108 --> 36:09.309
If Shen Haoming

36:09.829 --> 36:11.469
secures Baraikin's collaboration,

36:11.949 --> 36:12.869
he'll probably

36:12.869 --> 36:13.909
enter the board.

36:14.188 --> 36:15.389
A quadruple victory.

36:15.949 --> 36:16.668
Are you done?

36:17.548 --> 36:18.148
Almost.

36:19.269 --> 36:20.389
I just want to remind you.

36:20.869 --> 36:21.869
In business,

36:22.909 --> 36:24.588
always be cautious.

37:07.869 --> 37:08.548
Mr. Shen,

37:09.508 --> 37:11.588
the three-month evaluation starts now.

37:12.349 --> 37:15.028
We hope to partner with Jinda.

37:16.389 --> 37:17.068
Me too.

37:18.028 --> 37:19.389
Both Xu Yan and I are thrilled

37:19.789 --> 37:21.188
to see you again in China.

37:22.508 --> 37:23.909
How are you two going?

37:24.949 --> 37:25.749
We've reconciled.

37:26.228 --> 37:26.989
She'll arrive soon.

37:37.789 --> 37:40.068
Sorry I'm late.

37:40.989 --> 37:41.708
Mr. Baraikin.

37:42.068 --> 37:42.749
Yan.

37:42.869 --> 37:44.429
We were just mentioning you.

37:44.628 --> 37:45.429
Long time no see.

37:45.429 --> 37:45.989
Darling.

37:46.188 --> 37:47.789
Happy to see you.

37:48.949 --> 37:50.548
I've been overwhelmed

37:50.548 --> 37:51.429
with work lately.

37:51.708 --> 37:52.749
I should've visited you.

37:53.148 --> 37:53.749
No worries.

37:53.989 --> 37:55.989
Brought some tea for you
and Mr. Baraikin.

37:56.228 --> 37:56.749
Thank you.

37:56.789 --> 37:57.989
You're so kind.

37:58.789 --> 37:59.588
Let's sit and chat.

37:59.949 --> 38:00.989
I want to sit

38:01.068 --> 38:01.628
with Sophia.

38:02.148 --> 38:03.389
You remembered my real name?

38:03.588 --> 38:04.508
Why can't I remember?

38:06.068 --> 38:07.588
You've lost a lot of weight.

38:07.708 --> 38:08.469
Really?

38:10.389 --> 38:11.108
Ms. Xu.

38:12.068 --> 38:12.749
I've heard about

38:12.749 --> 38:13.989
your company's trouble.

38:14.349 --> 38:15.628
Fortunately, you went through.

38:16.429 --> 38:16.949
Yes.

38:17.628 --> 38:19.068
Thanks to your wife.

38:19.349 --> 38:20.909
She wore Yan Studio's gown

38:21.309 --> 38:23.389
and gave us such a strong endorsement.

38:23.668 --> 38:25.028
So, we have this success now.

38:25.228 --> 38:25.829
Not really.

38:25.829 --> 38:27.389
Yan Studio's designs are exceptional.

38:30.068 --> 38:31.869
I saw Mr. Shen's interview too.

38:32.228 --> 38:33.548
His vision and integrity

38:33.588 --> 38:34.869
truly impress me.

38:36.789 --> 38:39.548
Men like us in business circles

38:39.789 --> 38:41.548
may dominate the outside world,

38:42.309 --> 38:43.869
and many cherish their wives.

38:44.269 --> 38:46.349
But to be like Mr. Shen,

38:46.949 --> 38:48.548
who admits his wife outshines him,

38:49.108 --> 38:49.949
that's truly rare.

38:51.269 --> 38:51.749
Thank you.

38:52.829 --> 38:53.588
Indeed.

38:53.708 --> 38:55.068
Back then, Mr. Shen

38:55.108 --> 38:57.228
asked me to choose a gown at Yan Studio.

38:57.269 --> 38:58.108
I knew

38:58.228 --> 38:59.309
he wanted to help you.

38:59.869 --> 39:01.309
I told my husband

39:01.668 --> 39:03.708
that they couldn't be in conflict.

39:04.349 --> 39:05.429
If you don't love someone

39:05.469 --> 39:06.628
with sincerity,

39:07.188 --> 39:07.949
you can't possibly

39:07.949 --> 39:08.949
be so considerate.

39:11.028 --> 39:11.668
I'm flattered.

39:12.108 --> 39:12.989
I should do so.

39:13.668 --> 39:14.148
Yan.

39:14.749 --> 39:15.989
Let's have a toast.

39:34.148 --> 39:35.909
I do need to thank my husband.

39:37.668 --> 39:39.028
He's been secretly

39:39.068 --> 39:40.548
doing a lot of things for me.

39:41.148 --> 39:41.989
And he even

39:42.028 --> 39:42.989
hid some to me.

39:46.829 --> 39:47.548
Haoming.

39:49.508 --> 39:50.228
I toast to you.

40:01.829 --> 40:02.349
Honey.

40:02.668 --> 40:04.749
If your collaboration succeeds,

40:05.148 --> 40:06.068
you must invite them

40:06.108 --> 40:07.389
to visit our home in Russia.

40:07.749 --> 40:08.188
Okay?

40:08.188 --> 40:08.668
Sure.

40:09.548 --> 40:10.588
You're welcome to come.

40:11.349 --> 40:12.668
He says you're welcome.

40:13.108 --> 40:13.628
Thank you.

40:14.869 --> 40:15.548
Have some more.

40:15.749 --> 40:16.188
Let's eat.

40:21.909 --> 40:23.188
Thank you for today.

40:23.909 --> 40:24.309
Right.

40:24.548 --> 40:25.148
Don't forget

40:25.228 --> 40:26.188
to order my gown.

40:26.668 --> 40:27.508
Don't worry.

40:27.588 --> 40:29.269
We'll have it custom-tailored.

40:29.749 --> 40:30.789
But it might take...

40:30.869 --> 40:31.829
Let's meet

40:31.949 --> 40:32.829
at the conference.

40:33.269 --> 40:34.228
Looking forward to it.

40:34.349 --> 40:35.309
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

40:36.708 --> 40:37.708
Goodbye, Mr. Baraikin.

40:37.749 --> 40:38.108
Goodbye.

40:39.508 --> 40:39.869
Okay.

40:43.148 --> 40:44.028
Goodbye.

40:44.349 --> 40:44.789
Goodbye.

40:46.469 --> 40:46.989
Goodbye.

40:50.028 --> 40:51.148
The wine tonight was good.

40:51.269 --> 40:51.829
Yes.

40:58.148 --> 40:58.989
I'm going back.

41:00.028 --> 41:00.548
Yan.

41:00.909 --> 41:02.588
I've finished the acting.

41:03.228 --> 41:04.148
Let me explain.

41:04.389 --> 41:05.148
Mr. Baraikin

41:05.148 --> 41:06.108
gave Jinda Group

41:06.148 --> 41:07.429
a three-month evaluation period?

41:13.668 --> 41:14.869
Don't explain to me.

41:17.829 --> 41:18.989
You did help me,

41:21.429 --> 41:22.429
but you also achieved

41:22.829 --> 41:23.668
your own purpose.

41:26.989 --> 41:28.628
To secure this collaboration,

41:29.349 --> 41:30.789
you skillfully used

41:30.829 --> 41:32.068
those around you.

41:32.749 --> 41:33.749
Typical of you.

41:35.349 --> 41:36.749
You haven't changed.

41:39.668 --> 41:40.469
But now you can

41:40.469 --> 41:41.349
finally relax.

41:43.148 --> 41:43.668
Fine.

41:44.708 --> 41:45.389
I admit it.

41:46.949 --> 41:48.349
I had Mrs. Baraikin

41:48.389 --> 41:49.668
wearing a gown from Yan Studio

41:50.309 --> 41:51.668
and had that interview,

41:52.068 --> 41:54.269
just to impress Mr. Baraikin.

41:54.628 --> 41:55.749
But I invited you here

41:55.789 --> 41:57.028
not to put on an act.

41:59.708 --> 42:00.668
Yet Mr. Baraikin

42:00.708 --> 42:01.429
still saw

42:01.508 --> 42:03.429
what you wanted him to see, right?

42:03.829 --> 42:04.668
What?

42:05.869 --> 42:06.749
Do you mean everything

42:06.749 --> 42:07.508
between us

42:07.708 --> 42:08.588
during this period

42:08.588 --> 42:09.469
was all fake?

42:13.389 --> 42:14.068
Doesn't matter.

42:18.668 --> 42:19.469
What matters is

42:19.469 --> 42:19.989
if we keep

42:19.989 --> 42:21.188
arguing like this,

42:22.909 --> 42:23.909
the paparazzo you hired

42:23.909 --> 42:24.708
might capture

42:24.749 --> 42:25.588
undesirable photos.

42:34.429 --> 42:35.628
Chen Lin, come here.

42:47.429 --> 42:47.989
Mr. Shen.

42:48.389 --> 42:48.909
Yan.

42:49.588 --> 42:50.349
I've deleted

42:50.708 --> 42:51.588
all his photos.

42:52.349 --> 42:53.429
I didn't mean

42:53.469 --> 42:54.749
to take photos of you.

42:55.789 --> 42:56.708
Take him away.

42:58.989 --> 42:59.349
Come on.

43:03.469 --> 43:04.628
That guy was sneaking around.

43:04.668 --> 43:05.989
I wondered what he was doing.

43:09.469 --> 43:10.548
Am I that stupid

43:11.749 --> 43:13.588
to hire such an amateur
for sneak photos?

43:14.108 --> 43:15.269
Chen Lin is better.

43:19.548 --> 43:20.148
I understand.

43:21.068 --> 43:22.668
The collaboration with Mr. Baraikin

43:22.749 --> 43:24.309
is crucial for Jinda Group.

43:25.909 --> 43:27.389
But someone's exploiting

43:27.429 --> 43:28.548
our relationship

43:29.508 --> 43:30.909
to sabotage your overseas market.

43:32.949 --> 43:34.309
Someone's targeting me?

43:35.148 --> 43:35.949
That Steve guy

43:38.228 --> 43:39.588
has approached me multiple times.

43:41.148 --> 43:41.749
I know.

43:42.349 --> 43:43.469
His backing company

43:43.469 --> 43:44.389
is Situo Company,

43:44.749 --> 43:46.028
with a shady background.

43:47.749 --> 43:49.228
He's just their frontman puppet.

43:49.228 --> 43:50.789
But I don't know

43:50.789 --> 43:51.909
who's truly behind it.

43:57.309 --> 43:59.068
That's not my concern,

43:59.068 --> 43:59.789
but yours.

44:01.789 --> 44:02.949
I've repaid your favor.

44:04.749 --> 44:06.068
Wish you go smoothly

44:06.068 --> 44:06.749
in business.

44:07.949 --> 44:09.068
When did I ever ask you

44:09.068 --> 44:09.829
to repay my favor?

44:09.829 --> 44:10.789
Am I that kind of man?

44:10.789 --> 44:11.548
I'd like to know

44:11.548 --> 44:12.869
who exactly you are.

44:18.588 --> 44:20.188
But I never figured it out.

44:24.588 --> 44:25.909
Now I finally understand.

44:31.829 --> 44:32.909
If you want to help me,

44:33.789 --> 44:35.148
I'll accept it graciously.

44:36.869 --> 44:38.309
We're adults after all.

44:38.708 --> 44:40.628
It's quite normal
to go after mutual benefit.

44:42.108 --> 44:43.469
As for you and I,

44:44.429 --> 44:46.269
let's just take what we need.

44:51.668 --> 44:53.068
We can still be friends.

44:55.909 --> 44:56.389
Take care.

